Class ClusterWheatleySoftDerivativesBD

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.virial.ClusterWheatleySoftDerivativesBD
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClusterAbstract, ClusterAbstractMultivalue
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClusterWheatleyMultibodyDerivativesBD

    public class ClusterWheatleySoftDerivativesBD
extends java.lang.Object
implements ClusterAbstract, ClusterAbstractMultivalue
    This class calculates the sum of all biconnected clusters using Wheatley's recursive formulation.
